    "notes": [
      "One-player JS oracle canary for Game.onStart scheduling PrintManager.start after 3000 ms.",
      "The scenario runner invokes Game.onStart after forced state, then advances its controlled timer queue by 2999 ms and 1 ms.",
      "Before 3000 ms, p0 remains printing=false with an inactive PrintManager and no trail/body point.",
      "At 3000 ms, PrintManager.start sets active=true, copies the current avatar position into lastX/lastY, calls setPrinting(true), emits the important point/property side effects, and sets deterministic print distance 39.",
      "Both ticks use step_ms=0 so the only promoted state change is the delayed timer start plus the source zero-step position event."
    ]
  },
